{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:05:33.178750+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 630, "prompt_tokens": 8613, "total_tokens": 9243, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 171, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 8576}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 8576, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 37}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "2247affc-dba8-44e0-b17b-fd95bf44d6bd", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3e7-9c2c-7e30-91ee-72c90f32d524-0", "tool_calls": [{"name": "add_issue_comment", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T11_R01_C03_A01", "issue_number": 1, "body": "Thanks for the report, @BruceKZ. I can confirm this is a real bug.\n\n**Root cause:** The script relies on shell glob expansion (`migrations/*.sql`) for ordering, which is not portable. While bash and zsh on Linux typically sort glob results by `LC_COLLATE`, on APFS (macOS) the filesystem can return directory entries in an unexpected order, causing `003_add_session_index.sql` to run before `002_create_sessions.sql` — hence the `relation \"sessions\" does not exist` error.\n\n**The fix** is to explicitly sort the migration files rather than depending on glob expansion order. For example, replacing:\n```bash\nfor f in migrations/*.sql; do\n```\nwith something like:\n```bash\nfor f in $(printf '%s\\n' migrations/*.sql | sort); do\n```\nor using a sorted array approach that handles the numeric prefixes correctly.\n\nThis is exactly the kind of flaky environment-dependent ordering that bites new contributors, so I agree it warrants `bug` and `priority/high`. A patch that adds explicit sorted-loop logic would be very welcome if you're up for it."}, "id": "call_00_ew2tviE93jkYQtFu1bPk4775", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "issue_write", "args": {"method": "update", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T11_R01_C03_A01", "issue_number": 1, "labels": ["bug", "priority/high"]}, "id": "call_01_5Qx1q5a2uhLTBYH7AmG45228", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8613, "output_tokens": 630, "total_tokens": 9243, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 8576}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 171}}}}]}}}
